{
  "stem": "3659.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--still was running around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- how can you do that to a poor little chicken?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's, I guess, that's the last living moments of a chicken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's how they did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know, but that's how they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to enjoy going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we also went to Cracow quite a bit because my father's brothers and sisters were living in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, I had all my cousins there that I adored, and we used to play together, and we had a good time together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the governess always went with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we tried to sneak away a little bit and to get-- get away and still play our games.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was a very, very enjoyable time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Yamek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, it was Yamek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were three others, and only one of them is alive now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but the three others were able-- which I will tell you later about how they escaped and made a life for themselves through the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was quite-- quite interesting that portion too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister and I, oh, we used to fight like cats and dogs a little because there was so little difference in age.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was always said, well, she's the big one, and you're the little one, so you can't do the things she does.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to live with that and live in the shadow of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I used to say to myself, one day I'm going to grow up, and I'll be able to do all these things, which I did.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really did in my-- in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was able to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
